This license is only applicable to all developers of based Minecraft development,Or its related games.
"Related Games" included but not limited to Minecraft:Bedrock Edition  Minecraft:Dungeons Minecraft:Education Edition.
"Based Minecraft" included but not limited to Mod,Translate.
The Minecraft Creator License is not only for all developers, but also for users who user this game.

This license can coexist with other licenses.

Considering the different languages, the Chinese and English versions will be used.
考虑到语言不同，将会采用中英对照。
Minecraft does not recommend any third-party extensions,However, this agreement still protects the creator of any third party's legal expansion.
Minecraft不引荐任何第三方的扩展,但本协议仍保护任何第三方合法扩展的创造者。

		1.Non-commercial
		1.非商业性
All Minecraft-based software and applications should not be commercial.
所有的基于Minecraft的软件与应用都不应该有任何的商业性。
The " commercial"  include: 商业性包括:
I.Payment mode of free software. 免费软件的付费模式
II.Fully payment software. 完全付费的软件
III.Accept software with conditional donation. 接受有条件捐助的软件
IV.Software payment after trial period. 试用期后付费的软件
V.Open source paid software 开源付费的软件
VI.Download free, but use paid software. 下载免费，但使用付费的软件
The "commercial" exclude: 商业性不包括:
I.Minecraft and related games. Minecraft和相关游戏
II.Develop software that requires periodic costs. 开发需要定期成本的软件（如公益公网)
III.Software that accepts unconditional donations. 接受无条件捐助的软件
IV.Public welfare projects 公益项目
V.Open source and free software 开源且免费的软件
VI.Do not accept any sponsored software 不接受任何赞助的软件
		2.lawful
		2.合法的
Any software that endangers users and servers cannot appear in the community.
任何危害用户、服务器的软件都不能出现在社区中。
For mod and clients beyond Vanilla,Legal without damaging the server.
对于超越Vanilla的模组、客户端,在不损坏服务器的情况下合法。
It is illegal for mod or client to contain a huge threat to the server and client.
mod或客户端里含有对服务端、客户端有巨大威胁功能的不合法。
The tool that performs press test on the server is legal after declaring that malicious behavior is prohibited, and vice versa.
对服务器进行压力测试的工具，在声明禁止恶意行为后合法，反之不合法。
The robot and crawler software related to Minecraft are legal.
与Minecraft相关的机器人、爬虫软件合法。
Developers who do not respect the original author or do not comply with the original author's open source license are not included in the scope of protection.
不尊重原作者或不遵守原作者开源许可证的开发者不在保护范围内。
ALL LEGITIMATE CREATORS SHOULD ENJOY RIGHTS.
所有合法的创作者应当享有权力。
[SPECIAL] FOR SOFTWARE THAT HAS BEEN PARTIALLY TAMPERED WITH, THE DEVELOPER CAN APPLY FOR CANCELLATION OF THE AGREEMENT.
[特殊]对于部分被篡权开发的软件，开发者可申请取消协议。
[SPECIAL] THIS LICENSE IS AVAILABLE TO THOSE WHO ARE ILLEGAL AND LEGAL AFTER CORRECTION.
[特殊]对于原本不合法在改正后合法的可享受本许可证。
