		4.Source Code
		4.源代码
Both Mojang and this license encourage open source.
无论是Mojang还是本许可证都鼓励开源。
The author of the source code enjoys copyright, even if he is illegal.
源代码的作者享有著作权，即使他不合法。
IN ANY CASE, ANY CLIENT AND SERVER LOSSES CAUSED BY OPEN SOURCE LEGAL SOFTWARE SHOULD BE BORNE BY ITSELF.
在任何的情况下，开源合法软件造成的任何客户端、服务端损失都应该自行承担。


